{
  "video_id": "Gg5M3J_FHXY",
  "title": "Simple hacks for life with Parkinson's | Mileha Soneji",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12800.0,
      "end_time": 15816.0,
      "text": "In India, we have these huge families."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15840.0,
      "end_time": 18416.0,
      "text": "I bet a lot of you all must have heard about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18440.0,
      "end_time": 21280.0,
      "text": "Which means that there are a lot of family events."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21840.0,
      "end_time": 25720.0,
      "text": "So as a child, my parents used to drag me to these family events."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26360.0,
      "end_time": 29375.0,
      "text": "But the one thing that I always looked forward to"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29400.0,
      "end_time": 31439.0,
      "text": "was playing around with my cousins."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32159.0,
      "end_time": 34455.0,
      "text": "And there was always this one uncle"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34480.0,
      "end_time": 35736.0,
      "text": "who used to be there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35760.0,
      "end_time": 37616.0,
      "text": "always ready, jumping around with us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37640.0,
      "end_time": 39136.0,
      "text": "having games for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39160.0,
      "end_time": 41959.0,
      "text": "making us kids have the time of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42920.0,
      "end_time": 45256.0,
      "text": "This man was extremely successful:"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45280.0,
      "end_time": 47280.0,
      "text": "he was confident and powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47920.0,
      "end_time": 52320.0,
      "text": "But then I saw this hale and hearty person deteriorate in health."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53240.0,
      "end_time": 55520.0,
      "text": "He was diagnosed with Parkinson&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56760.0,
      "end_time": 60815.0,
      "text": "Parkinson&#39;s is a disease that causes degeneration of the nervous system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60840.0,
      "end_time": 63816.0,
      "text": "which means that this person who used to be independent"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63840.0,
      "end_time": 69800.0,
      "text": "suddenly finds tasks like drinking coffee, because of tremors, much more difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69800.0,
      "end_time": 72456.0,
      "text": "My uncle started using a walker to walk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72480.0,
      "end_time": 73696.0,
      "text": "and to take a turn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73720.0,
      "end_time": 77776.0,
      "text": "he literally had to take one step at a time, like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77800.0,
      "end_time": 79390.0,
      "text": "and it took forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80240.0,
      "end_time": 83416.0,
      "text": "So this person, who used to be the center of attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83440.0,
      "end_time": 85496.0,
      "text": "in every family gathering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85520.0,
      "end_time": 87600.0,
      "text": "was suddenly hiding behind people."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88400.0,
      "end_time": 91760.0,
      "text": "He was hiding from the pitiful look in people&#39;s eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92440.0,
      "end_time": 94520.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s not the only one in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95280.0,
      "end_time": 100776.0,
      "text": "Every year, 60,000 people are newly diagnosed with Parkinson&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100800.0,
      "end_time": 102840.0,
      "text": "and this number is only rising."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104360.0,
      "end_time": 109776.0,
      "text": "As designers, we dream that our designs solve these multifaceted problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109800.0,
      "end_time": 112616.0,
      "text": "one solution that solves it all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112640.0,
      "end_time": 114920.0,
      "text": "but it need not always be like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115680.0,
      "end_time": 118496.0,
      "text": "You can also target simple problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118520.0,
      "end_time": 122440.0,
      "text": "and create small solutions for them and eventually make a big impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123120.0,
      "end_time": 126496.0,
      "text": "So my aim here was to not cure Parkinson&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126520.0,
      "end_time": 129696.0,
      "text": "but to make their everyday tasks much more simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129720.0,
      "end_time": 131120.0,
      "text": "and then make an impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 135600.0,
      "text": "Well, the first thing I targeted was tremors, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 136440.0,
      "end_time": 140976.0,
      "text": "My uncle told me that he had stopped drinking coffee or tea in public"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 141000.0,
      "end_time": 142479.0,
      "text": "just out of embarrassment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143000.0,
      "end_time": 146480.0,
      "text": "so, well, I designed the no-spill cup."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147800.0,
      "end_time": 149936.0,
      "text": "It works just purely on its form."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149960.0,
      "end_time": 155216.0,
      "text": "The curve on top deflects the liquid back inside every time they have tremors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 155240.0,
      "end_time": 158800.0,
      "text": "and this keeps the liquid inside compared to a normal cup."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 158800.0,
      "end_time": 163720.0,
      "text": "But the key here is that it is not tagged as a Parkinson&#39;s patient product."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 164400.0,
      "end_time": 168456.0,
      "text": "It looks like a cup that could be used by you, me, any clumsy person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 168480.0,
      "end_time": 172480.0,
      "text": "and that makes it much more comforting for them to use, to blend in."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 173920.0,
      "end_time": 176576.0,
      "text": "So, well, one problem solved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 176600.0,
      "end_time": 177840.0,
      "text": "many more to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 178640.0,
      "end_time": 181550.0,
      "text": "All this while, I was interviewing him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 181800.0,
      "end_time": 182616.0,
      "text": "questioning him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 182640.0,
      "end_time": 186335.0,
      "text": "and then I realized that I was getting very superficial information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 186360.0,
      "end_time": 189176.0,
      "text": "or just answers to my questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 189200.0,
      "end_time": 192359.0,
      "text": "But I really needed to dig deeper to get a new perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 193000.0,
      "end_time": 196736.0,
      "text": "So I thought, well, let&#39;s observe him in his daily tasks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196760.0,
      "end_time": 199120.0,
      "text": "while he&#39;s eating, while he&#39;s watching TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 199800.0,
      "end_time": 203856.0,
      "text": "And then, when I was actually observing him walking to his dining table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 203880.0,
      "end_time": 209550.0,
      "text": "it struck me, this man who finds it so difficult to walk on flat land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 209800.0,
      "end_time": 210800.0,
      "text": "how does he climb a staircase?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 211320.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "Because in India we do not have a fancy rail that takes you up a staircase"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 215400.0,
      "end_time": 217550.0,
      "text": "like in the developed countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 217800.0,
      "end_time": 219200.0,
      "text": "One actually has to climb the stairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 219920.0,
      "end_time": 221176.0,
      "text": "So he told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 221200.0,
      "end_time": 223200.0,
      "text": "\"Well, let me show you how I do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 223880.0,
      "end_time": 225920.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a look at what I saw."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 228960.0,
      "end_time": 231616.0,
      "text": "So he took really long to reach this position,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 231640.0,
      "end_time": 233495.0,
      "text": "and then all this while, I&#39;m thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233520.0,
      "end_time": 235456.0,
      "text": "\"Oh my God, is he really going to do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235480.0,
      "end_time": 238375.0,
      "text": "Is he really, really going to do it without his walker?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 238400.0,
      "end_time": 239600.0,
      "text": "And then ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 242280.0,
      "end_time": 244600.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 248680.0,
      "end_time": 250840.0,
      "text": "And the turns, he took them so easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 253240.0,
      "end_time": 254480.0,
      "text": "So -- shocked?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 254920.0,
      "end_time": 256399.0,
      "text": "Well, I was too."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 259320.0,
      "end_time": 262296.0,
      "text": "So this person who could not walk on flat land"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 262320.0,
      "end_time": 264400.0,
      "text": "was suddenly a pro at climbing stairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 265720.0,
      "end_time": 270375.0,
      "text": "On researching this, I realized that it&#39;s because it&#39;s a continuous motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 270399.0,
      "end_time": 273536.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s this other man who also suffers from the same symptoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 273560.0,
      "end_time": 274976.0,
      "text": "and uses a walker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275000.0,
      "end_time": 277960.0,
      "text": "but the moment he&#39;s put on a cycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 277120.0,
      "end_time": 278816.0,
      "text": "all his symptoms vanish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 278840.0,
      "end_time": 280919.0,
      "text": "because it is a continuous motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 281560.0,
      "end_time": 285856.0,
      "text": "So the key for me was to translate this feeling of walking on a staircase"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 285880.0,
      "end_time": 287280.0,
      "text": "back to flat land."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 287880.0,
      "end_time": 290816.0,
      "text": "And a lot of ideas were tested and tried on him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 290840.0,
      "end_time": 294359.0,
      "text": "but the one that finally worked was this one. Let&#39;s take a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 297440.0,
      "end_time": 300496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 300520.0,
      "end_time": 304976.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 305000.0,
      "end_time": 306456.0,
      "text": "He walked faster, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 306480.0,
      "end_time": 309680.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 311240.0,
      "end_time": 314160.0,
      "text": "I call this the staircase illusion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 314400.0,
      "end_time": 318616.0,
      "text": "and actually when the staircase illusion abruptly ended, he froze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 318640.0,
      "end_time": 320656.0,
      "text": "and this is called freezing of gait."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 320680.0,
      "end_time": 321896.0,
      "text": "So it happens a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 321920.0,
      "end_time": 325856.0,
      "text": "so why not have a staircase illusion flowing through all their rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 325880.0,
      "end_time": 328240.0,
      "text": "making them feel much more confident?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 329440.0,
      "end_time": 332960.0,
      "text": "You know, technology is not always it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 332120.0,
      "end_time": 334896.0,
      "text": "What we need are human-centered solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 334920.0,
      "end_time": 337136.0,
      "text": "I could have easily made it into a projection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 337160.0,
      "end_time": 339496.0,
      "text": "or a Google Glass, or something like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 339520.0,
      "end_time": 341840.0,
      "text": "But I stuck to simple print on the floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 342360.0,
      "end_time": 345296.0,
      "text": "This print could be taken into hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 345320.0,
      "end_time": 347719.0,
      "text": "to make them feel much more welcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 348600.0,
      "end_time": 351696.0,
      "text": "What I wish to do is make every Parkinson&#39;s patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 351720.0,
      "end_time": 354176.0,
      "text": "feel like my uncle felt that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 354200.0,
      "end_time": 357880.0,
      "text": "He told me that I made him feel like his old self again."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 359120.0,
      "end_time": 363120.0,
      "text": "\"Smart\" in today&#39;s world has become synonymous to high tech,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 363960.0,
      "end_time": 367120.0,
      "text": "and the world is only getting smarter and smarter day by day."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 367800.0,
      "end_time": 371480.0,
      "text": "But why can&#39;t smart be something that&#39;s simple and yet effective?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 372320.0,
      "end_time": 376296.0,
      "text": "All we need is a little bit of empathy and some curiosity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 376320.0,
      "end_time": 378575.0,
      "text": "to go out there, observe."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 378600.0,
      "end_time": 380496.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s not stop at that."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 380520.0,
      "end_time": 384176.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s find these complex problems. Don&#39;t be scared of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 384200.0,
      "end_time": 387776.0,
      "text": "Break them, boil them down into much smaller problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 387800.0,
      "end_time": 390296.0,
      "text": "and then find simple solutions for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 390320.0,
      "end_time": 393336.0,
      "text": "Test these solutions, fail if needed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 393360.0,
      "end_time": 395520.0,
      "text": "but with newer insights to make it better."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 396240.0,
      "end_time": 400496.0,
      "text": "Imagine what we all could do if we all came up with simple solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 400520.0,
      "end_time": 404000.0,
      "text": "What would the world be like if we combined all our simple solutions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 404880.0,
      "end_time": 407896.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s make a smarter world, but with simplicity."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 407920.0,
      "end_time": 409136.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 409160.0,
      "end_time": 412200.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}